headline: GTA Online
subtitle: New Special Races
content: You might think you’ve mastered every concept car and experimental prototype the showrooms of Los Santos have to offer. But the truth is that in the fine art of hovercar, jetpack, and submersible racing you’re still an amateur, and there’s only one way to turn pro. Beat the best in this new batch of fiendish special races, and you’ll have nothing left to prove.
